{"tid":141730,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[去旅行睇風景]你係屬於邊種人?","createTime":"2017-03-03T06:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T12:13:17.000Z","uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"90e48972ab4351c9a66cb8890dea69ea0ff04511","tid":141730,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:56:37.000Z","msg":"唔計旅行要食好野，住得好，或者購物派<br />\n只計景點派，風景派<br />\n<br />\n1。務求去哂行程plan好既景點，時間比較趕，所以每個景點逗留唔可以太耐<br />\n<br />\n2。寧願喺鍾意既景點留耐啲，影到一張靚靚冇人既風景相，但放棄其他既景點"},{"pid":"03f581b0ba6101d97a4fc6f2b243bede0d0803a4","tid":141730,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:57:57.000Z","msg":"2.<br />\n走馬看花去咗等於冇去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b5795f6b4461a4bca1222ff3ba783a9c6eebef","tid":141730,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:10:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2.<br />\n走馬看花去咗等於冇去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實兩難局面<br />\n又驚冇下次，冇機會再去<br />\n但趕進度又好辛苦"},{"pid":"3e7b9e4d5e93b75900c31b3b7dece3dc0d857ad9","tid":141730,"uid":32213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:12:40.000Z","msg":"積極尋求中間路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會慢慢看慢慢行<br />\n但又唔會為了影相留好耐<br />\n用眼看過體會過就夠"},{"pid":"cf59884ed8779f0e748b59202c431fab8eb7d26f","tid":141730,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:15:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>積極尋求中間路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會慢慢看慢慢行<br />\n但又唔會為了影相留好耐<br />\n用眼看過體會過就夠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n假期多咪ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一日一景點<br />\n但可惜邊有咁多假<br />\n<br />\n以前我都覺得眼看過就夠<br />\n但十年後會後悔<br />\n因為人腦會忘記<br />\n後悔當初點解唔影多啲相"},{"pid":"f06c9f6df12851cca39c0e0caead0741ce0c5c4a","tid":141730,"uid":81751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:20:51.000Z","msg":"唔係走馬看花咁睇但又會一日三四個景點咁去"},{"pid":"5d475456d29e9a667a1c909817f81832a1c7aacc","tid":141730,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:13:17.000Z","msg":"1.去多幾個地方<br />\n我寧願早d起身，再排密d<br />\n都想去晒想去既地方<br />\n<br />\n去第二次先再深度旅遊"}]}